  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Recurrent urinary tract infections (UTI) are a problem for postmenopausal women. The aim of
      this trial is to evaluate the effectiveness of lactobacilli in combination with low dose
      estriol for preventing recurrent urinary tract infections in postmenopausal women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
